{
  "texts": [
    "The use of Desktop 6DOF HMD devices are recommended, so that user movements can be monitored.",
    "The development of training-related experiences will depend on the objective.",
    "For example, if the training is oriented towards mental skills such as interaction through motor imagery, EEG is necessary as an interaction method.",
    "And if the objective is to train the user in decision-making under pressure, sensors that measure HR and respiration may be more useful (e.g., Michela et al. 2022).",
    "In any case, the applications must be Interactive or with a very limited exploration of the environment which distracts users from the tasks."
  ]
}